Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:14.53,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,They say seven out of ten high school\N couples break up within a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If you include after graduation, \Nalmost all of them are destined to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:25.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Even so, people still get swept up in love.\N In the tears. In the laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't have a lot of confidence,\Nin reality or in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:34.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,that I'll ever find my world changed\N by a fleeting relationship like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.33,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But sometimes, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:44.04,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I actually did have an \Nexperience like that in my teens?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:47.87,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I did find a teary-eyed \Nheroine standing before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.82,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I was the main \Ncharacter in a light novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.28,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.25,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,what would I think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:06.25,Flashback,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You did your best, big brother!\NI know it must've been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:10.63,Italics,Kurumi & Nukumizu,0,0,0,,"I know all about how dedicated you are."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.37,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,"So if you need anyone to lean on, \Nyour little Kurumi is right here for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:24.84,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, this is so good. \NAnd I'm finally about to get to the climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.73,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Every book in this series has twenty pages\Nof the lead getting totally pampered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.44,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,You can't, Sosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:32.48,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,You can't be wasting time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.15,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:37.00,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,They're in my class. \NThat's Yanami Anna and Hakamada Sosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.66,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Why are they having a lovers' \Nquarrel in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.49,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,If you don't go see her now, \NKaren-chan is gonna leave for England!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Don't you care about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Karen must be that girl \Nwho transferred recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.26,Flashback,Karen,0,0,0,,A-ha! You're that molester from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.76,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,She's already transferring again?\N And to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.72,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The story's moving way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.81,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,But Karen... already said goodbye to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:04.12,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,That obviously means she \Nwants you to go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.14,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,How would you know—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Because I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:11.40,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I mean, that's how I've always \Nfelt about you, Sosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.01,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.01,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Go to her. Karen-chan's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.33,Default,Sosuke,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:39.30,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Don't apologize to me, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.31,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just pretend \NI didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.93,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,N-No! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:01.09,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Stop! That's so painfully desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.40,Default,Employee,0,0,0,,Miss! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.33,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I didn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.88,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Sosuke and I have been friends\N since we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.04,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,He made me a ring out of white clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.21,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,He said he'd make me his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,His wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,His wife... His wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yanami-san, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.95,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,For now, just drink that \Nand try to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:03.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're in my class... \NNukumizu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.14,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh? You're asking me that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,This is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's rosehip tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.42,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be good for the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.52,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,For my skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.87,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone to show it off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.23,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Stop! Too graphic for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.65,Default,employee,0,0,0,,Extra large fries. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.77,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.60,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What? I didn't order that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.20,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,You're fine with honey mustard \Nand cod roe mayo for sauces, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.14,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Did you order that, Yanami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.04,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Karen-chan's a dear friend of mine. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:38.06,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But you know, she just\N transferred here in May!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.88,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Don't the twelve years I've known \NSosuke count for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:46.17,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'll ask one more time. \NWas it you who ordered the fries?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:51.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Sosuke said he'd make me his wife. \NIsn't that mean? What a liar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.85,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,When exactly did he say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:59.61,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,It was before elementary school, \Nso we must've been about four or five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.65,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yeah, that doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Wait. Does this mean he's cheating on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.75,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Were you and Hakamada actually dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh. I guess it probably looked that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:13.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So you weren't even going out? \NThen it's not cheating at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.21,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I-I mean, it was basically like \Nwe were half-dating, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:21.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,And if that soggy cow hadn't waltzed onto\N the scene, we'd probably still be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Wasn't she a "dear friend" a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.38,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:30.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,If I'd worked up the courage sooner, \Nthings might not have turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.32,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,W-Well, you might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.01,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm such a mess today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.82,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, it's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.56,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That's not what you need to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.78,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:46.79,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,As long as Sosuke's happy, I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.69,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What a spectacular reaction \Nto getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:56.50,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Speaking of, there's a term that \Nperfectly describes girls like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yanami Anna. Yes, it fits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You're a "losing heroine."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:08.28,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1400)\an8\fnGeorgia\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\fs40\c&H6B1437&\pos(170.667,70)}Too\N{\fnVerdana\fs50\c&H608EF7&}Many
