Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.56,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Few realize that the flavor of water\N changes depending on the faucet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.70,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I am one of those who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,In the morning, the water from \Nthis faucet really is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's the farthest one from \Nthe water tank on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.86,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,so the water has a much \Nlower chlorine content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:40.39,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Once I've had my fill, I calculate the distance\N and time it'll take me to get back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:46.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If I get back too soon, I may find someone\N in my seat, and that'd be annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.13,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.88,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But someone's in my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:54.69,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot. I guess that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.85,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\bord0\shad0\b1\fs16\frz7.747\pos(238,208.666)\c&HBBC0AF&}4th Period: World History \Nwill start 10 minutes late.\NIndependent study \Nuntil then!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:04.91,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh. Looks like the archery team made it \Nto nationals for the third year in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.22,Top,Karen,0,0,0,,Okay, then the three of us \Nshould eat lunch together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.11,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.74,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.34,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Sosuke, be sure to take \Ngood care of Karen-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:14.66,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.29,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,You really are my best friend, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:22.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Even though she calls you a "soggy cow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, maybe Yanami's over it by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.63,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Wow. Yeah, she's not over anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.72,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hey, Yanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,U-Um, you're on duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.33,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Amanatsu-sensei's asking for you \Nto go help in the printing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.57,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, did you \Nsay that to help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.57,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.08,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.84,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Another second and I'd have had \Na death grip on Karen-chan's boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,How can she say that with a straight face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.54,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, remember \Nhow I paid for you on Friday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.83,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I don't have my wallet on me, but maybe you \Ncan meet me at the emergency stairs at lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:12.80,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,The fire escape staircase. \NIn the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.12,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Sure. As long as you pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.47,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,You know, they actually started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.94,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,So why did they ask me to \Neat with them? It's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,And here I thought we were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.69,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're trying \Nto hurt me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.73,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Are you guys seriously best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.66,Top,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Hey! Yanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.70,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Class is about to st—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.29,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Amana-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.75,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.71,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Amanatsu-sensei, aren't these \Nthe wrong lesson materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.24,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't know who you think you are,\N but get it together, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:56.00,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,In second year, we cover the \NByzantine Empire! Viva Byzantine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.99,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Sensei, your next class is 1-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.14,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.06,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,And I'm actually one \Nof your students, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:04.75,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Byzantine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Not Byzantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.08,Default,female student,0,0,0,,Isn't that wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Please save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:26.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Karen-chan wants the three of us to\Ngo do karaoke together after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.67,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,They're gonna make me \Nlisten to them sing a duet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:35.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, are you \Nsaying you want me to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.47,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, no... Uh, good luck, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.22,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So about the money from before—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.43,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I even got a message from Sosuke's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.65,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,"I can't get a hold of Sosuke. \NAre you two together?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.65,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Now, why in the world didn't\N he see her messages? I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.07,Italics Top,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Somebody save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.11,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.49,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.52,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I can't talk about this with any \Nof my friends or acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.29,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Guess that means I'm not\N even an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:12.04,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So... do you think you can \Nfinally pay me back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.05,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Here's the receipt from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.23,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks so much for that.\N You really saved my—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.96,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Did the total go up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:25.30,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yanami-san, you also got an order\N of watermelon pancakes, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:25.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.54,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,And you finished up with\N a pork shabu udon salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,'Cause salads don't make you gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.02,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm not opposed to your faith\N in salads. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:39.53,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,It's just an idea, but what if I were \Nto repay you in some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.94,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:48.66,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm not actually very good at it, \Nso I'm not sure if it'll satisfy you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.46,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,but Sosuke used to say he really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.51,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,She can't possibly mean \Ndoing something wet and sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.42,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No way! This is bad! And we're at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.34,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.30,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Listen—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.69,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm not very good at cooking, \Nbut I think I could manage a bento lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.05,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,A bento lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.37,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, right! A bento lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But one bento lunch \Nprobably won't cover it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:18.50,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Right, so I'll make you one every day \Nuntil it equals the amount on the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.86,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm not sure—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.33,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll start tomorrow.\N I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.66,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\b1\shad0\fs11\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\frz301.8\pos(471.333,98.666)}Receipt
