Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord4\shad0\fs10\fscx90\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\pos(386.667,112)\frz296.9}Extra Large French Fries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord4\shad0\fs11\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\pos(366.667,107.333)\frz296.6}Steak Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord4\shad0\fs11\fscx90\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\frz296.6\pos(359.334,129.333)}Hamburg Steak Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs11\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\frz295.1\pos(344,136)}Salad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs11\blur0.3\fax-0.0.5\c&H393D2C&\3c&HA3A590&\frz295.1\pos(331.333,140.667)}Soup
