Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs18\blur0.3\fnArial\fax-0.2\pos(266.001,184.667)\frz292.5\c&H393D2C&}Total
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.89,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.88,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,U-Um, you're N-Nukumizu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.61,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm, um, a first-year \Nin the literature club—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.64,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh? Who? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.77,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,Um, my name is Komari. \NFrom the literature club. Komari Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:12:00.02,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,U-Um, I need to speak with you!\N A-About the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:03.33,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,With me? What does the \Nliterature club want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.83,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,W-Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.54,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, you're in the lit club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:13.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:15.59,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:22.68,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Just after I started here, I think I got talked\N into signing up for the literature club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:30.17,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,"The student council sent out a warning about \Nmembers who aren't participating in the club"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:34.12,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, right? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.87,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I apologize. I think I've \Nbeen ghosting for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.28,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It helps a lot having you back, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.26,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I'm the vice president, Tsukinoki Koto.\N Third-year. Remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.39,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Of course I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.34,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Not a bad selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:57.25,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You can borrow whatever you want. \NJust don't touch the Dazai or Mishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.21,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The student council has had \Ntheir eyes on us recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.34,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\pos(289.333,170)\c&H020500&}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:00.46,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\c&H020500&\pos(321.333,171.333)}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:00.59,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\c&H020500&\pos(350,170.666)}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:00.71,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\c&H020500&\pos(410,169.999)}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:00.84,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\c&H020500&\pos(469.333,169.332)\clip(m 471 224 l 473 154 418 127 384 150 388 187)}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:00.96,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs18\fnGeorgia\b1\frz316.1\c&H020500&\clip(m 471 224 l 473 154 418 127 384 150 388 187)\pos(499.333,171.332)}You are \Nthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.43,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to hang out \Nwith us for a while. Okay, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.64,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Absolutely do {\i1}not{\i0} touch \Nthe Dazai or Mishima, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:29.58,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The BL genre aside, at least there's a \Nbunch of popular series I haven't read yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.95,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't need to worry about \Nlunch money for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:37.03,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Maybe I can hold off on new books and catch \Nup on a few series the lit club doesn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.94,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,100)\an8\fnTimes New Roman\fax-0.2\fs15\bord1\shad0\c&H59618B&\pos(521.333,148)\3c&HE0E5E3&\frz359.3}\hNew Paperback \NReissue Lineup
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.46,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,You definitely have to buy \N{\i1}You're the Innocent Queen of Darkness{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.62,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,At least up to volume 5, when my favorite \Ncharacter starts turning to the dark side—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.59,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Kaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.54,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Why are you in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:50.56,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,I'm in here most of the time. \NYou just don't notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What a creepy thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.60,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,So, big brother, have you \Nmade any friends at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:03.52,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,Have no fear, big brother. I, Kaju, \Nwill find you some friends without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.79,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,First of all, I'll make you a chara-ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.74,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Kmff-rhf-bmf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:12.43,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,Yes! A character bento's a great \Nconversation starter that'll win people over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:17.73,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I've actually got someone \Nmaking lunch for me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.75,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,B-B-Big brother, are you saying\N you're going out with a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.76,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:25.76,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,Oh, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.55,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,How could someone with \Nno friends have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:33.94,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange to have a non-friend \Nnon-girlfriend making lunch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.20,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, I've actually paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.19,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,Oh, eating out with a working girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:44.61,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,It must be one of those "bento lunch" things.\N My friends told me all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.47,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Kaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.69,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You need to find better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.69,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Isn't that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.08,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.54,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm talking about you! \NI asked for your help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.59,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I had to listen to the brand-new \Ncouple singing duets together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.25,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Can you imagine how that felt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.53,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So what about my lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.68,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.07,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.14,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I tried to make two bento \Nlunches this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:22.02,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,and my mom was like, \N"I'm sure Sosuke-kun will be thrilled!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.42,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,This is convenience store food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.31,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't make enough for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.54,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The packaging's clearly \Nhandmade, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.51,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's say this is 268 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.13,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Too cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.06,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But that's the actual price.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.18,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Fine. 300 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:46.76,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Anyway, why don't you keep \Nyour distance from those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Everyone's walking on eggshells\Naround me in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:55.49,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,'Cause, like, Sosuke and I used \Nto be together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:59.56,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,"Oh, what? Did Yanami get dumped?" \NThat's the vibe right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:03.16,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not sure what to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.67,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Okay, 350 yen.
