Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.85,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,I heard you joined the lit club, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.88,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,My teacher told me they have \Nthe complete works of Abe Kobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.70,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Can I borrow them sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.42,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, that's probably okay. \NI'll check with my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:23.92,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.63,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:30.34,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,I'm skipping my club today. \NWanna go get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.69,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Sorry. I have prep school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.94,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Huh? You're still a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:38.14,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,If all you do is study, \Nyou're just gonna get dumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.63,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,And if you don't study more, \Nyou'll end up repeating the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:46.06,Default,Chihaya,0,0,0,,Mitsuki-san. We're going to be late \Nto cram school if we don't get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.65,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Oh, Chihaya. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.24,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,See you later, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.16,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh... Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:58.25,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Hey, are you and Mitsuki friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Uh, we're not exactly friends, \Nbut we go to the same cram school—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.17,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,So do you know who that girl was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:08.60,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um, Asagumo-san, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,She and Ayano are both\Ntaking the advanced course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.70,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Advanced course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.68,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,I guess Mitsuki's into smart girls after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.84,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Lemon-chan, what are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.19,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Huh? N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.80,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,It's just, we've been in the same \Nclass since elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.37,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.45,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.90,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,That woman is the homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.82,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. "Homewrecker"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Listen, Nukumizu-kun, \Nthere are only two types of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.20,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,The childhood friend and the homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But what a contrast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.98,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Hey, what do those two look like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:51.09,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,They seem pretty friendly, \Nbut didn't they meet just recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.18,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Maybe they're just plain friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.61,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Right! I'm sure they're just plain friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.43,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,I knew you'd get it, Yana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Lemon-chan, I kinda feel like \Nwe're not that different after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.81,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.15,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,They're asking me to hang out again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.13,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,"Wanna come study at Karen-chan's house?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.49,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You should say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But if I don't go, \Nit'll be just the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That may be true, but where's my lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.57,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, you ever think this \Nmight be why you don't have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.71,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't need that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.74,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Hold the lid a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:38.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I only have one lunch box I can use, \Nso I shoved the two servings into one box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.09,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Okay, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.30,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, how much is that worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um, let's say 400 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.97,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nice! Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:52.64,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,At this rate, I should be able to \Npay it off by summer vacation.
