Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.37,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,You can see the field from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.06,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.65,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Isn't that Lemon-chan over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Lemon-chan... She sure is fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.78,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I heard she placed in the \Nprefectural competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.27,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,How'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.09,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm no slouch when it comes to \Nreading the announcement board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.67,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Lemon-chan's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.57,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I guess I really got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:45.61,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I understood it in my head, but I don't \Nthink my body had figured it out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:50.37,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I was here thinking, \N"Wow, Lemon-chan sure can run."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:54.18,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,And then it turned into \N"Wow, I sure got dumped."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:21:00.78,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, maybe if you get dumped flat \Non your face someday, you'll know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.37,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:07.07,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Still, nothing changes after you've been dumped. \NDoesn't even feel like a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.55,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But still, everything around\N you keeps moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,so you've got to keep moving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:17.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I've never been dumped before, \Nso I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.42,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Spoken like a lady-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:31.11,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,They say seven out of ten high school\N couples break up within a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:36.19,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If you include after graduation, \Nalmost all of them are destined to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:41.91,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Even so, people still get swept up in love.\N In the tears. In the laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.63,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't have a lot of confidence,\Nin reality or in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:51.42,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,that I'll ever find my world changed\N by a fleeting relationship like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.61,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But sometimes, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.90,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I actually did have an \Nexperience like that in my teens?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:04.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I did find a teary-eyed \Nheroine standing before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.59,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What if I was the main\Ncharacter in a light novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.55,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If that happened...
