Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.98,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\fs25\an8\fnGeorgia\c&HE9E9E9&\t(0,400,\c&HB2B1B5&)\t(400,800,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(800,1200,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(1200,1600,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(1600,2000,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2000,2400,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(2400,2800,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2800,3200,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(3200,3600,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(3600,4000,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\pos(320,245)}Professional Childhood Friend Yanami Anna's\N Style of Losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.28,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,what would I think about it?
